e\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a daily mental ritual\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"her nerves\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence mode\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"four to five pages\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"every competition\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am feeling so much in the moment,\\\" Lee tellsFortuneabout her competition-day nerves.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"score\": 0.9509557747020566, \"rank\": 0.05156526831325583, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"her competition-day nerves\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee, who has partnered with pharmaceutical giantEli Lilly and Company, a health equity sponsor of Team USA, says \\\"I like to write down my keywords, trying to remember my why, things that I need to remember when I am out there competing and simple things like just telling myself affirmations and to breathe because that's something that I struggle with when I am competing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1117, \"end\": 1120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"score\": 0.9509557747020566, \"rank\": 0.05156526831325583, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999638246285572, \"rank\": 3.585010577148453e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pharmaceutical giantEli Lilly\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"Company\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"a health equity sponsor\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"my keywords\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"competing and simple things\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"affirmations\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, Lee was diagnosed with an incurable kidney disease that forced her to take a training hiatus.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"score\": 0.9509557747020566, \"rank\": 0.05156526831325583, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an incurable kidney disease\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"a training hiatus\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she kept her sights on the Olympics and worked with her medical team to make a comeback, which she recalls in anInstagram postas \\\"so much more than my return to elite gymnastics.\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her sights\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"her medical team\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"a comeback\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"anInstagram postas\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1735}, {\"ngram\": \"my return\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"elite gymnastics\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was me proving to myself that I can overcome hard things, and to hopefully inspire others to never let life's setbacks stop you from going after your dreams.\\\"\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hard things\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1845}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"life's setbacks\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"your dreams\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then, reminding herself to breathe and relax has become more integral to her training routine.\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her training routine\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mindfulness also helps strengthen the brain and tune the mind for performance.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mindfulness\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"the brain\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"tune\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"the mind\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2113}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a practice touted bybillionaire Brad JacobsandStarbucks CEO Laxman Narasimhanfor optimizing performance and fighting burnout.\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2196, \"end\": 2202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lakshmana\", \"score\": 0.9999965622437204, \"rank\": 3.4377519625315805e-06, \"text\": \"Laxman\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lakshmana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lakshmana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a practice touted bybillionaire\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2239}, {\"ngram\": \"burnout\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You are teaching yourself to be nonjudgmentally aware of the present moment,\\\" Elizabeth Seng, an associate professor of psychology at the Ferkauf Graduate School of Psychology at Yeshiva University, previously toldFortune.\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2342, \"end\": 2351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"score\": 0.9107269194778573, \"rank\": 0.09779471869150788, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\"}, {\"begin\": 2443, \"end\": 2461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yeshiva_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yeshiva University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yeshiva_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yeshiva_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the present moment\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2339}, {\"ngram\": \"an associate professor\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2380}, {\"ngram\": \"psychology\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"the Ferkauf Graduate School\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2425}, {\"ngram\": \"Psychology\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"previously toldFortune\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Journaling self-affirmations also triggers the brain's reward system, which can \\\"be a powerful vehicle for turning down the brain's stress alarm system,\\\" Dr. David Creswell, a professor of neuroscience and psychology at Carnegie Mellon University and researcher in self-affirmations, previously toldFortune.\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2707, \"end\": 2733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carnegie_Mellon_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.235475575190229e-25, \"text\": \"Carnegie Mellon University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carnegie_Mellon_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carnegie_Mellon_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Journaling self-affirmations\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2515}, {\"ngram\": \"the brain's reward system\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2555}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerful vehicle\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2589}, {\"ngram\": \"the brain's stress alarm system\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2638}, {\"ngram\": \"a professor\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"neuroscience\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2688}, {\"ngram\": \"psychology\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2703}, {\"ngram\": \"researcher\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"self-affirmations\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2769}, {\"ngram\": \"previously toldFortune\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lee repeats a saying and journals a 10-word phrase before competing: \\\"Nothing more, nothing less because your normal is good enough.\\\"\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2796, \"end\": 2799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"score\": 0.9509557747020566, \"rank\": 0.05156526831325583, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a saying\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"journals\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"a 10-word phrase\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2846}, {\"ngram\": \"Nothing\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a phrase that she has leaned on during the most intensive training periods and competitions.\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 3028, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a phrase\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2944}, {\"ngram\": \"the most intensive training periods\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 3010}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's super important to me because I know when I was younger, the community around gymnastics wasn't as positive as it is now,\\\" she says, adding that you have to accept dealing with more failures than successes.\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3241, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3105}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3123}, {\"ngram\": \"more failures\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3225}, {\"ngram\": \"successes\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carving out time for mental preparation has helped boost Lee's confidence, which she recalls being challenged amid various health struggles while competing over the years.\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3300, \"end\": 3303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"score\": 0.9509557747020566, \"rank\": 0.05156526831325583, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3259}, {\"ngram\": \"mental preparation\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3282}, {\"ngram\": \"various health struggles\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3382}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was always looking at myself like 'Oh, my gosh.\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can see my eczema, or do I look really strong right now?'\\\"\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my eczema\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"she says.\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\